Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  志贵先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐吃日式的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要喝的东西就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐一定要吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的身体比上学更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果又因为贫血而昏倒怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有食欲的话吃稀饭好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我马上去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么搞的嘛  秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不是才因为翘课教训了我一顿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功课方面请个家教就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有意见请你努力稍微早一点起床如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来哥哥终于习惯远野家的生活了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↓Title↓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:13.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,275)}{\fad(0,500)}白之梦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心秋叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐没有发现志贵少爷每天晚上都出门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请慢走  志贵少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年B班的那群男生  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我三天前还在街上看过他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那一天起好像就没有回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是离家出走而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  你竟然不知道这件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一样糊里糊涂的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是离家出走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很不平静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙以前常常深夜到处玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会被吸血鬼干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的啦  只是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来想点快乐的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天几点集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事不能去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟远野有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来是有约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人不要再去理她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像学姐说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我收敛一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上十点在车站集合没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样约定了喔  远野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的迟钝已经构成犯罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓冢和Ciel学姐的感觉都变得很奇怪不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多该说清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在装傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过不要到学校来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去看电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天不是有开吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候哪有时间做那种像是约会一样的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去志贵家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被谁误会？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好机会  我去打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很怕你妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想让她担心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要去看电影就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是为了玩才跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭菜都没有动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合你的口味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话一起喝杯餐后茶好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去准备点心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然琥珀好像喜欢伯爵红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.47,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵红茶：EarlGray英国调味茶  以中国红茶为基础  加上佛手柑熏制而成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我还是喜欢大吉岭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.92,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉岭：Darjeeling  印度著名红茶  在过去  大吉岭茶的得奖高于一切其他红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太懂红茶的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块栗子蛋糕味道怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是琥珀亲手用花园里的栗子做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听翡翠说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥想要一台电视
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说就可以了  不用客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我叫人送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁挂型的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶你不是讨厌吵闹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不过  哥哥有需要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做点让步也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你学了这么多东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语会话、钢琴、小提琴还有茶道和插花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是删减过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前还有学芭蕾和书法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为大小姐还真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你也去学一两样如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作身为远野家长男的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说差不多该去念书了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也会想用功的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试也快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久我峰先生打电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是为了玩才跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是生我的气自己先走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是邀请我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要跟我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫作搭讪  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是打工的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次再麻烦你了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚你到底在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到当模特儿这么好赚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问什么事  你怎么会去打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是需要钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也不用特地去打那种工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地想请你好好吃一顿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛这么生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有死者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年B班的那群男生对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野  你想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经不是你的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他早就已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想请你吃点好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有这份心就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么弄错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为志贵是个彻头彻尾的杀人狂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始不就说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一个平凡的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想帮忙也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…  218
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的伤不是还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就更不能放着你不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说些不像你会说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在勉强自己吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说不是勉强自己应该算是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我说过要帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  志贵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要到那上面去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵的学校在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个山丘上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要打什么奇怪的主意喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心  放心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真的变了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来对你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道得不多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底从什么时候开始存在的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是八百年前左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八百年？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟人类不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活八百年这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是活着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵  我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尝试下约会
