Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要躲避的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆的破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人晕眩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:24:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  真月谭月姬“苍之罪痕”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我担心哥哥
